OL,3,CCouple in their 90s say they 'have no
OL,4,Cchoice' to sell home to pay for care
OL,6,FRoy and Shirley Sharp told ITV News
OL,7,FMeridian's John Ryall that the sale of
OL,8,Ftheir Sevenoaks home will pay for
OL,9,Fabout two and a half years of care.
OL,11,FRoy and Shirley Sharp from Sevenoaks
OL,12,Fin Kent, both in their 90s, are
OL,13,Fselling their home so they can get the
OL,14,Fcare they need.
OL,16,FIt costs them #3000 a week and the
OL,17,Fpeople running the care home say they
OL,18,Fhave no choice but to raise the fees
OL,19,Fagain to make ends meet.
