OL,6,F"We are launching an independent
OL,7,Fcommission with Louise Casey, one of
OL,8,Fthe best known reformers in Whitehall,
OL,9,Fand we're going to work cross-party
OL,10,Fbecause isn't a shortage of good ideas
OL,11,Fbut there is a shortage of good
OL,12,Fpolitics."
OL,14,F"I've been encouraged by the
OL,15,Fwillingness of the Conservatives, the
OL,16,FLiberal Democrats and Reform to work
OL,17,Ftogether with the Labour Government to
OL,18,Fdo something truly historic for our
OL,19,Fcountry, that will benefit future
OL,20,Fgenerations."
