OL,6,FBut Roy and Shirley Sharp, who are
OL,7,Fhaving to sell their home to meet the
OL,8,Fcosts of their #3000 a week care, are
OL,9,Fnot impressed.
OL,11,F"You grasp the nettle firmly and make
OL,12,Fa decision quickly, not in three, four
OL,13,For five years time," said Mr Sharp.
OL,15,FThey believe the solution is a major
OL,16,Fnew tax to raise the billions of
OL,17,Fpounds needed.
