OL,6,F"I would love to see an announcement
OL,7,Fthat recognises the severe pressure
OL,8,Fthat social care is under and a
OL,9,Frecognition of that additional
OL,10,Finvestment in our sector needs,
OL,11,Ftargeted where it's most needed," said
OL,12,FMr Norman.
OL,14,F"And that is to transition people out
OL,15,Fof hospital, supported where they can
OL,16,Fin their own home, in a way that gives
OL,17,Fthem the maximum choice possible."
