OL,6,FThe National Care Association welcomes
OL,7,Fthe social care commission announced
OL,8,Ftoday, and the cross-party approach,
OL,9,Fbut says 2028 - probably close to the
OL,10,Fnext general election - is way too
OL,11,Flong to wait for reform.
OL,13,F"We know that social care needs
OL,14,Fsomething right now so 2028 seems a
OL,15,Flong, long, time for us to wait before
OL,16,Fthey make a decision about what might
OL,17,Fbe needed when we already know that
OL,18,Finvestment is one of the key things
OL,19,Fthat's needed," said Nadra Ahmed from
OL,20,Fthe National Care Association.
